headline.main: Express Scripts Cuts Ties to New York Specialty Pharmacy
headline.print_headline: Express Scripts Cuts Ties to a Specialty Pharmacy

docs.abstract: Express Scripts sends termination letter to Woodbury, NY, pharmacy Linden Care signaling immediate end to their business relationship; spokesman says action was taken because Linden Care seemed to mostly dispense expensive drugs made by Horizon Pharma; Linden Care sues Express Scripts in retaliation.

headline.main: India Is Caught in a Climate Change Quandary
headline.print_headline: India, Facing Climate Change, Also Desperately Needs More Energy

docs.abstract: Eduardo Porter Economic Scene column emphasizes how scientist, environmentalists, world leaders and business executives attending upcoming Paris climate change talks must figure out how to deal with India; notes India will be one of hardest hit nations by effects of climate change, and asserts convincing case must be made for country to eschew fossil-fuel-heavy path out of poverty while balancing its domestic demands for development.
